    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"checked the amendments\" yourself? I didn't realize you had direct access to the regional force communications. That’s a pretty heavy claim. I'm just worried because some of the raw data feeds we pay for are showing high volatility in the northern sector. If you're so sure it's just bad drone imagery, can you walk me through the specifics of why those troop movements are definitely just equipment errors? I need to be able to defend this if the board asks for proof of why we're dismissing the field reports.",
